Description: Xbase database SQL interface
DescDetail: <<
Xbase is a collection of specifications, programs, utilities and a
C++ class library for manipulating Xbase type datafiles and indices.

XBSQL is a wrapper library that provides SQL access to Xbase.  It
supports select, insert, update, and delete.  There is also a
limited ability to use indexes.
<<
